task.summary: A nasty navigating kludge to handle differing application paths on badger vs. laptop
working version getting fancytree and search to work
simple kludge to prevent chrome from submitting form
moved click() to outside of once() so that the click event is sent every time.
decorating fancytree elements with popovers straightened out click handling to solve problem of "second click not responding" by moving drupal ajax trigger to custom "navigate" event
reimplemented search button by triggering new "doSearch" event in search field.
added renderNode to markup the span properly for Drupal Ajax Some Search box css tweaks
Fixed Tree-mangling bug, by turning off autoScroll.
